Megax is a Grizzard - a giant monster-eating powerhouse, the biggest and most 
powerful Grizzard known. He breathes fire, unleashing devastating flames that 
travel across the arena. As the mightiest of all Grizzards, Megax brings 
incredible strength and size to the arena, making him a formidable opponent 
with his unique fire breath attacks and massive presence.
